{"tid":2286490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"同志婚姻｜已婚同志提繼承遺產司法覆核遭政府上訴 丈夫隨時被房署趕走 律師：配偶過世連屍體也領取不了","createTime":"2020-11-15T04:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T09:13:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8caca69a58fcc449184c2b4f06f83455ae2dcad","tid":2286490,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"家人朋友都十分支持兩小口，Henry不斷強調：「我們真的十分幸運。」可是兩人剛成婚不久，已面對很多白眼，「我們在英國結婚，當時已經有尷尬的狀況，就是應不應該將結婚照放到網上。其實真的很古怪，結婚那麼喜悅的事，我們卻會考慮應不應該跟人分享。」兩人決定回港後再公開婚照，好讓跟親朋好友解釋，怎料英國朋友率先把照片上載祝福，Henry說：「他們對同性婚姻沒有忌諱，就將照片放到網上，之後我們看到有人在照片按嘔嘔表情符號，按憤怒表情符號，有很多難聽的留言，令我們很傷心。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201115/3VITHY5FEZHKNNK5BNEKLKRO4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201115%2F3VITHY5FEZHKNNK5BNEKLKRO4A%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=3e2f4761\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201115%2F3VITHY5FEZHKNNK5BNEKLKRO4A%2F&h=854abf02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201115/3VITHY5FEZHKNNK5BNEKLKRO4A/</a>"},{"pid":"d2c1523549c96e7520ef7b1df2bf7de85d066c85","tid":2286490,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"466297bc0d2b44fe7fc6d5fa6030ca6c380f1c00","tid":2286490,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:12:26.000Z","msg":"國際大都會已經成為笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d437f66c29d837b566fd74dc7e70ea65defd98","tid":2286490,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}